You were a big help to Ulaa.

Skritt thank u -
U made a gurd matey, matey. U help skrit whu cant swim in hot . U help skrit wh b lazy, u help skritt whu get atakd bi grien fiir thigs. Mayb sumday u teach skrit how to writ betr. 

(The rest of the writing on this letter is too illegible to read. Still, the fact that A skritt took the time to write a letter of thanks is endearing.)

Thank you for your aiding the Makali community, %str1%.

Life is difficult out here on the edge of the Crystal Desert, but having an outlander volunteer their time to protect and aid our nomad friends is inspiring to all of us at the outpost. You are welcome back here anytime. Good fortune.

â€”Nuri, Cavalier Scout
